.org/resource/Anthony_Bamford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Bamford\"}, {\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998404223461, \"rank\": 1.5957765603040353e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has put in such a lot of hard work over the last 20 years it really is truly deserved.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very proud of his achievement and delighted to have played a small part in his success.\\\"\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam said:  \\\"I am so proud to represent JCB on the biggest sporting stage.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being from Staffordshire myself too makes the connection extra special.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Staffordshire\", \"score\": 0.9999999950051688, \"rank\": 3.2075965296435513e-09, \"text\": \"Staffordshire\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Staffordshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Staffordshire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The JCB support has enabled me to focus entirely on my training and recovery since before Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Backhoe\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.046653412504979e-13, \"text\": \"JCB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Backhoe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Backhoe\"}, {\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9932717264424655, \"rank\": 0.005938175911530639, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \